Heads up!
~~~~~~~~~
- The finally() function is replaced by ensure($t) - see pull request #187
  This way we're forward-compatible with PHP 5.5 - see issue #186.
  http://news.planet-xp.net/article/481/2012/09/30/
  (friebe)
- The SAPI feature is now deprecated and will be removed in next major series!
  (friebe)
- Changed newinstance() to declare classes inside the package of the 
  base class (or interface)
  (friebe, kiesel)
- Changed lang.reflect.Field::getType() to return lang.Type instances.
  Added getTypeName() to restore old behaviour. See issue #34.
  (friebe)
- Merged pull request #93: Access to private constructors, methods and fields
  (friebe)

